## ğŸ› ï¸ Installation

### ğŸ“¦ PyPI

Install the package from PyPI:

```bash
pip install sortium
```

Alternatively, install from source:

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/Sarthak-G0yal/Sortium.git
cd Sortium

# Install in editable mode
pip install -e .
```

